@devinleighsmith uncovered some false positives in the output of these test results; https://github.com/hyperledger/indy-plenum/actions/runs/726586406, which are based off the merge of the [Upgrade Ubuntu 20.04](https://github.com/hyperledger/indy-plenum/pull/1522) work.  The plenum test slices are falsely passing because `runner.py` was not updated for the newer python version and was not detecting any tests; so the jobs are passing because no tests are run at all.

